    },
    {
      "span_id": "p059_s0014",
      "text": "Fabric Address Notification (FAN)",
      "bbox": [
        133.8,
        358.96,
        294.33,
        370.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p059_s0015",
      "text": "4.2.15.1  Description",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        382.96,
        192.63,
        394.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p059_s0016",
      "text": "The FAN ELS shall be sent by a Fabric  F_Port (FFFFFEh) to all known previously logged in (via",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        406.96,
        539.92,
        418.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p059_s0017",
      "text": "FLOGI) attached NL_Ports following an initialization event. This initialization event is typically Loop",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        418.96,
        539.77,
        430.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p059_s0018",
      "text": "Initialization on an Arbitrated Loop, though other events that may cause a port to change its ID may",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        430.96,
        539.96,
        442.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p059_s0019",
      "text": "also be considered. The F_Port Controller shall report the F_Port_Name and Fabric_Name as they",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        442.96,
        539.95,
        454.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p059_s0020",
      "text": "were reported in the prior FLOGI, and shall report the current Loop Fabric Address. The F_Port Con-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        454.96,
        539.93,
        466.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p059_s0021",
      "text": "troller shall send this ELS using the default login parameters (i.e., the parameters that are in effect",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        466.96,
        540.08,
        478.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 6,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p059_s0022",
      "text": "prior to a FLOGI Request).",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        478.96,
        214.33,
        490.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 7,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p059_s0023",
      "text": "The attached ports may use this information to authenticate active Exchanges and operating param-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        502.96,
        540.04,
        514.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p059_s0024",
      "text": "eters (e.g., login BB_Credit).",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        514.96,
        222.04,
        526.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p059_s0025",
      "text": "The F_Port Controller shall report identical information to all attached NL_Ports. If the information",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        538.96,
        539.89,
        550.08
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p059_s0026",
      "text": "changes in any way before the F_Port Controller is able to send the service to all attached ports, the",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        550.96,
        540.03,
        562.08
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p059_s0027",
      "text": "F_Port Controller shall begin a new initialization event.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        562.96,
        336.49,
        574.08
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p059_s0028",
      "text": "The attached NL_Ports shall not initiate a Reply Sequence to this ELS.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        586.96,
        408.8,
        598.08
      ],
      "block_index": 14,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
